      • getBundleName

        protected String getBundleName()
        Description copied from class: ODataLibraryException

        Gets the name of the ResourceBundle containing the exception texts.

        The key for an exception text is the concatenation of the exception-class name and the ODataLibraryException.MessageKey, separated by a dot.
